name: language_html_data_small_angle_element
description: |
  U+FE64 SMALL LESS-THAN SIGN and U+FE65 SMALL GREATER-THAN SIGN normalize to
  ASCII angle brackets under NFKC. This catches filters whose normalization
  order differs from the renderer or storage layer.
format: utf8-strip
decode-as: utf8
unicode-meta:
  code-units: 18
  code-points: 14
  scalar-values: 14
  legacy-grapheme-clusters: 14
  extended-grapheme-clusters: 14
tags:
  - "language"
  - "html"
  - "xss"
  - "xss-data"
  - "utf8"
  - "small-form-variant"
  - "angle-bracket"
  - "nfkc"
  - "normalization"
  - "inert-canary"
---
﹤x-xss-canary﹥
